SUMMARY:Spring into Summer New Menu & Cheesecake Vend-O-Rama is Here!
DESCRIPTION:Our new Spring into Summer Menu launches today & our Cheesecake Vend-O-Rama machine is stocked with fresh selections & Peanut Butter Pie\, to welcome Spring. Ask for a free sample of our handmade crystal gem candy {Khohakutou} when you stop in too! \n\n\n\nNestled in the heart of historic downtown Lancaster\, the Vintage Candy Shop offers a nostalgic trip down memory lane\, with hundreds of novelty and retro candies. Our ice cream counter serves hand-dipped local Kreider Farms ice cream\, sundaes & banana splits plus lots of vegan options & drinks made with Lancaster County Roasters Coffee. With a working vintage cigarette vending machine\, plus toy & candy quarter machines\, there’s something for everyone.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/spring-into-summer-new-menu-cheesecake-vend-o-rama-is-here/
LOCATION:Vintage Candy Shop\, 38 W King St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/cityoflancasterpa-242134369851055-6509023556841258723-FirstFriday_04-2026_1684.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Vintage Candy Shop":MAILTO:christine@beechtreetrading.com
END:VEVENT
