SUMMARY:First Friday Hours at the Lancaster Medical Heritage Museum
DESCRIPTION:Join us this Friday\, April 3rd\, for extended evening hours at the Lancaster Medical Heritage Museum. We’ll be open 4:00–8:00 PM\, in addition to our regular daytime hours. \n\n\n\nWhether you’re stopping in during your First Friday stroll or making a night of it\, it’s a great chance to explore Lancaster’s medical history after hours. \n\n\n\n$5 admission for all visitors. \n\n\n\nWe hope to see you there.
