SUMMARY:PCA&D Spring Art Market
DESCRIPTION:Join PCA&D for its Spring Art Market! Over 65 students and alumni of the college will be vending goods such as stickers\, prints\, pins\, knitted items\, jewelry\, altered clothing\, photos\, paintings\, and more. This year’s market will include live drawings and photobooths! Event runs 4-6pm. Students will accept digital payment via paypal\, cashapp\, and venmo. While cash may be accepted\, digital payment is preferred.
