SUMMARY:Lancaster Improv’s First Friday Free For All
DESCRIPTION:Two bite size shows followed by an improv jam where YOU can take the stage! \n\n\n\nTwo teams give you a taste of what improv can be\, then you take the stage to show them how it’s done! Whether you’re a storied veteran of the stage\, or a doing improv comedy for the first time\, you’ll be supported by the evening’s coach in attempting games and scenes. \n\n\n\nJoin us for a casual night out in downtown Lancaster City that will have you rolling in the aisles…well\, aisle! \n\n\n\nFREE to all! BYOB \n\n\n\nJam will start approximately at 8:30. \n\n\n\nLANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/lancaster-improvs-first-friday-free-for-all/
LOCATION:Lancaster Improv Players\, 16 S Prince St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:First Friday,Free Events and Activites,Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/First-Friday-No-Mixer.jpg
