DESCRIPTION:For almost 300 years people have been coming together to meet at Market to enjoy the freshest local food\, ready-made unique dishes and flavors from all over\, and special finds you can only get at Lancaster Central Market. Our building is a historic structure with history and beauty around every corner located in the heart of downtown Lancaster.
