SUMMARY:Challenging Ride (A) - EP Marietta 2 (37R)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nAnticipated average pace:
  **18-20 mph**\n\nhttps://ridewithgps.com/routes/29400627\n\n\\* We might 
 stop/detour for a quick warm up and coffee at Molly's Coffee Shop at mile 
 17\n\n**This is a Challenging (A) level ride and intended to be a NO DROP 
 RIDE.** The ride leader will ride at the advertised average speed and will
  do his/her best to keep the group together with regroupings and a sweeper
  may also be appointed at the start. **Please do not join this ride if you
  are not willing to stick with the group.** If maintaining an 18-20mph ave
 rage is beyond your current ability level\, please consider joining an "Ad
 vanced" ride first.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring wat
 er and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\
 n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we require an LBC 
 Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetu
 p does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https://www.lancasterbi
 keclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is your a
 greement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clu
 bexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\,\n\
 n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?pag
 e_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159)\, and [Ride Waiver](https://lanca
 sterbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=454318)
