SUMMARY:Intermediate Ride (C) - BV Brownstown Akron Farmersville Long (24F
 )
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\n**Be Safe\, Have Fun\, an
 d Ride Together**\n\nRide leader: Denine Chemnitz\nAnticipated Average Pac
 e: (14-16 mph)\nRoute: [https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/bv-browns
 town-akron-farmersville-long-24f/](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cu
 e/bv-brownstown-akron-farmersville-long-24f/)\n\nThis is an Intermediate C
  Class ride. The ride leader will ride at the advertised average speed. Th
 is is intended to be a group ride with a no-drop rule as the main goal. Th
 e ride leader will do his/her best to keep the group together with occasio
 nal regroupings and/or splitting into multiple groups to align to pace cap
 abilities.\n\nPlease do not join this ride if you are not willing to ride 
 with the group. If you exceed the posted pace\, you will be riding by your
 self and encouraged to join a faster group. If maintaining a 14-16 mph ave
 rage is beyond your current ability level\, please consider joining a slow
 er ride first.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring water an
 d a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo
  eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we require LBC Club mem
 bership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride. Being on Meetup does not 
 mean you are a club member. Join here [Member Signup](https://www.lancaste
 rbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148)\n\nYour RSVP is your
  agreement to abide by the club's Code of Conduct: [Code of Conduct](https
 ://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module
 _id=323984)\n\nGuidance if an incident occurs: [Incident Actions](https://
 lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=326
 137)
