SUMMARY:Creative Release Open Studio Saturday
DESCRIPTION:The Creative House of Lancaster\n#### ***A Place to Make Art T
 ogether***\n\n**When:** Every Other Saturday from 10am - 12pm\n**Where:** 
 [The Candy Factory](https://share.google/nqC7VtCS6IcDeBRyg)\n**Cost:** Fre
 e & Open to the Public\n**Ages:** All Ages\n\n**Upcoming Dates**\nApril 4\
 , April 18\, May 2\, May 16\, May 30\, June 13\, June 27\, July 11\, July 
 25\, Aug 8\, Aug 22\, Sept 5\, Sept 19\, Oct 3\, Oct 17\, Oct 31\, Nov 14\
 , Nov 28\, Dec 9\, Dec 23\n\n*Do you have creative aspirations but never s
 eem to make the time? Do you want the companionship of others to overcome 
 your creative blocks and “just do it”?*\n\nCreative Release provides s
 paces and resources that make artmaking accessible. Whether you’re an ex
 perienced artist or just looking to explore your creative side\, Creative 
 Release is a safe place to explore your ideas with others. Bring your ongo
 ing projects or use the art materials available.\n\nDon't have a project a
 t the moment? That's just fine. I’ll have materials to share.\n\n**What 
 to Expect:**\n\n* A welcoming\, inclusive environment\n* A variety of art 
 materials to experiment with\n* Demonstrations on how to use different art
  materials\n* The opportunity to work on your personal projects\n* The cha
 nce to meet and collaborate with fellow creatives\n* A moment to relax\, c
 reate\, and escape the usual routine\n\n**Who Should Join?**\nAnyone and e
 veryone! Bring an idea for a card\, a knitting pattern you’ve been wanti
 ng to try\, a shirt that needs mending\, or a full-on canvas and paints. M
 ost of all\, bring your lovely self! We believe in the power of community 
 and creativity.\n\n[Event Link](https://www.jodavis.art/community-events-1
 /creative-release)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/event
 s/314110354/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T192808Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T192808Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
