UID:08333c990c5f43ae35c971ef6c86957a@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nJoin local author Peter Belz f
 or a reading and discussion from his memoir\, Working Titles: Memoir of an
  American Hustler\, a true story told through sixty-six different jobs acr
 oss six decades. The program explores working-class labor\, reinvention\, 
 survival\, and the realities of building a life job by job. The event will
  include a short reading\, audience discussion\, and Q&A\, followed by an 
 on-site book signing and sales.Ages 18+ · Walk-ins welcome!
LOCATION:Lancaster\, LPL Community Room
