SUMMARY:FREE Music Saturdays at grandview with Ryan Moran
DESCRIPTION:Join us for LIVE music every Friday and Saturday evening from 6:00 pm – 8:30 pm. Experience joy and laughter with friends over a glass of your favorite wine\, local beer or specialty cocktails. Music will be held in our warm and cozy tasting room. We are open 12:00 pm – 9:00 pm Saturdays\, so plan to arrive early as seating is first come first serve. Food is available for purchase or you may bring your own. Beverages are available for purchase until 8:30 pm. No open bottles will be sold after 8:30 pm.
