  open\nCue and GPX link: [Brownstown Akron Farmersville Long](https://rout
 es.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/bv-brownstown-akron-farmersville-long-24f/)\n
 \nThis is a Casual (D) level group ride with an average of pace 12-14 mph.
  The intent of this and all LBC rides is to be safe\, have fun\, stay toge
 ther.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring water and a basic
  repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nWe require 
 LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP to join this ride.\nBeing on Meetup do
 es not mean you are a club member.[Join the Club](https://www.lancasterbik
 eclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148)\n\nYour RSVP is your agr
 eement to abide by the club's:\n[Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clu
 bexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\n[Ru
 les of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id
 =22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159)\n[Ride Waiver](https://lancasterbikec
 lub.net/docs.ashx?id=763523)
