DESCRIPTION:Book Club\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nAll are invited to join the Re
 aders' Roundtable for lively conversation and discussion! The book discuss
 ions for 2026 are as follows:January 5 - Wayward Girls by Susan WiggsFebru
 ary 2 - The Night Watchman by Louise ErdrichMarch 2 - Things You Save in a
  Fire by Katherine CenterApril 6 - My Brilliant Friend by Elena FerranteMa
 y 4 - Mother Daughter Murder Night by Nina SimonJune 1 - A memoir of you c
