UID:d5978374ea2240db86a92a7f1de843df@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Babies\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nIntroduce literacy
  and learning to your little one with a community in the Library! We will 
 occasionally make messy art\, including sensory experiences that are alway
 s optional. After reading a few stories we will enjoy lots of peer playtim
 e! This session will have Rachel Cox from Community Action Partnership in 
 Lancaster County! We will provide resources to families about the preschoo
 l transition\, healthy attachment styles and the importance of understandi
 ng your child's developmental performance.  We are a proud Family Place Li
 brary\, which our focus is on providing families with further education on
  their child and encouragement for partnership in the community. Ages 0-5.
