SUMMARY:Spring Bubble Bowl Arrangement Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Spend an evening creating\, learning\, and welcoming spring together. Our expert designer will walk you through the techniques behind a beautifully balanced bubble bowl arrangement — no experience needed. Bring a friend and enjoy a creative night out in our floral studio.\n\nClass Details:\n\nDate: Apr 8th\, 2026\nSession Times: 5:30 PM\nLocation: Central Market Flowers on Queen\nRegistration is required\, and spots are limited—so secure your place today! Whether you’re a flower enthusiast or a beginner looking to try something new\, this class is a perfect opportunity to learn from the best while having fun with flowers. \n            \n        \n                \n            \n                \n                \n    Learn More
