SUMMARY:Un Noche en Casa Blanca (Latin Inspired Girl's Night Out)
DESCRIPTION:Join Lancaster Women for Good for a relaxed and joyful evening celebrating culture\, connection\, and good food. We’re gathering on April 8th from 6 to 9pm for Una Noche en Casa Blanca\, a Latin-inspired night designed to bring us together in a fun and meaningful way. \n\nExpect a night that pulls you right into the spirit of Latin culture with bold flavors\, good drinks\, and a beginner-friendly Salsa or Bachata class that adds a little adventure to the evening. It’s the kind of experience that lets you unwind\, try something new\, and enjoy the moment. \n\nWednesday\, April 8th\,  2026\n6:00–9:00pm\nCasa Blanca Event Space — 201 W Orange St\, Lancaster\nTickets are $70 per person\nLatin-inspired dinner + beverages\nCash bar available\nFun beginner Latin dance class \n            \n        \n                \n                \n    Buy Tickets
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/un-noche-en-casa-blanca-latin-inspired-girls-night-out/
LOCATION:Casa Blanca Event Space\, 201 W Orange St\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603-3747\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://fig.guide/content/uploads/sites/3/2026/02/LCWG-GNO-Casa-Blanca-Apr-8.avif
