DESCRIPTION:Book Club\, Adults\n\nBring your appetite and a dish to share 
 to Read It and Eat: A Cookbook Club!Each month\, we will display the chose
 n cookbook at the Lancaster City Branch circulation deskRegister by adding
  your name and chosen recipe to the signup sheet (also located at the circ
 ulation desk)A staff member will make one (1) free photocopy of your chose
 n recipe\, or you can take a picture.Prepare the recipe for the Cookbook C
 lub potluck style meetingParticipants should follow all food safety precau
 tions when preparing their dish\, and all allergens should be clearly stat
 ed.At the meeting\, enjoy a potluck dinner while we discuss our experience
 s with the recipesDiscussion will center around baking/cooking techniques\
 , recipe clarity\, skill level\, and accuracy\, as well as ways to improve
  or change the recipe.
