 r desire for design and creativity. They will be given a challenge to comp
 lete\, and when they are finished\, they will get to choose a prize!
LOCATION:Manheim Community\, MAN Children's Area
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/lego-lab-154450
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
