  Adults\, Seniors\n\nExperience the mesmerizing process of pour painting i
 n our upcoming hands-on workshop! Participants will be guided through the 
 techniques of fluid art to create their own unique abstract masterpiece. T
 o ensure a cohesive and vibrant aesthetic for the class\, the instructor w
 ill pre-select a professional color palette for all projects.Note on Colle
 ction: Due to the necessary drying time for fluid art\, finished canvases 
 will be available for pickup starting Saturday\, April 11th. We kindly ask
  that you collect your artwork as soon as possible after this date.Please 
 wear your favorite 'artist’s outfit'—you know\, the one you don’t mi
 nd getting a little (or a lot!) of paint on!
