SUMMARY:An Evening with Jeff Foxworthy
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $89 $109 $129 $149 \nGet ready for a night of laughter with comedy legend Jeff Foxworthy — one of America’s best-loved stand-up stars. Foxworthy is the top-selling comedy-recording artist in history\, a multiple GRAMMY® nominee\, and the author of more than 26 books. He’s entertained audiences as the host of TV hits like Are You Smarter Than a 5th Grader? and appeared on NBC’s comedy competition series Bring the Funny. His comedy special “We’ve Been Thinking” is streaming on Netflix\, and he continues to headline tours across the country. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/an-evening-with-jeff-foxworthy/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/JF_Concessions-Events-and-News-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
