BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Fig Lancaster": "https://figlancaster.com/event/spring-fling-at-lancaster-friends-school/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:figlancaster
X-SOURCE:Fig Lancaster
X-SOURCE-URL:https://figlancaster.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T150000
DTSTAMP:20260403T224922
CREATED:20260313T120325Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T200349Z
UID:10014495-1775905200-1775919600@figlancaster.com
SUMMARY:Spring Fling at Lancaster Friends School
DESCRIPTION:Spring is in the air\, and that means it’s time for our favorite tradition: the Annual Spring Fling! Join us on April 11th at 1210 Maple Avenue in Lancaster from 11am-3pm for a day full of laughter\, live music\, local food\, and family fun – all in support of our mission of nurturing a peace-centered and socially conscious learning community. This year’s Spring Fling will feature: Local vendors and artisans showcasing unique\, handmade goods Live performances from area musicians and dance groups Games and activities for kids of all ages Delicious food from community favorites Silent auction Whether you’ve joined us in the past or you’re a first-time guest\, Spring Fling is the perfect way to connect with friends\, neighbors\, and our mission of nurturing a peace-centered and socially conscious learning community. Admission is free\, and all proceeds from our silent auction and ticketed activities go directly to funding educational programs and outreach initiatives that strengthen our community.Bring your family\, invite your friends\, and help us make this year’s celebration our biggest yet! Founded by members of the local Quaker community\, Lancaster Friends School was established to offer education rooted in the belief that “education is the way to lasting peace\, and there can be no peace without justice.” LFS embraces the Quaker testimonies of Simplicity\, Peace\, Integrity\, Community\, Equality/Equity\, and Stewardship/Sustainability\, known collectively as SPICES\, which guide both its educational philosophy and day-to-day practice. LFS serves children from preschool through eighth grade\, fostering an environment where curiosity\, compassion\, and conscience grow together in balance. \n\n\n\n\n    Learn More
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/spring-fling-at-lancaster-friends-school/
LOCATION:Lancaster Friends School\, 1210 Maple Avenue\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Festivals & Annual Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://fig.guide/content/uploads/sites/3/2026/03/Spring-Fling-Lawn-Sign-ver-2-1-scaled.avif
ORGANIZER;CN="Lancaster Friends School":MAILTO:acarty@lancasterfriends.org
END:VEVENT
