UID:10001829-1776020400-1776020400@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:Nitty Gritty Dirt Band - All the Good Times: The Farewell Tour - 60 Years of Dirt
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $39 $49 $59 $79\n \nNitty Gritty Dirt Band has been delighting audiences with their signature blend of country\, folk\, rock\, and roots music. Widely regarded as one of the most influential bands in American roots history\, their career spans multiple generations and includes timeless hits like “Mr. Bojangles\,” “Fishin’ in the Dark\,” “An American Dream\,” and “House at Pooh Corner.” \nThe All the Good Times Tour celebrates the band’s incredible legacy — from their groundbreaking Will the Circle Be Unbroken collaborations to their chart-topping radio favorites. With their trademark harmonies\, masterful musicianship\, and heartfelt storytelling\, The Nitty Gritty Dirt Band continues to prove that great music only gets better with age. \nJoining NGDB is emerging country artist Meels with her soulful voice\, heartfelt lyrics\, and modern country flair. Blending authentic storytelling with infectious melodies\, Meels is quickly capturing hearts and carving out her place in today’s country music scene. \nVIP1: The Nitty Gritty Front Row with Meet & Greet Experience   $305 \nIncludes: \n\nPremium reserved ticket in the front row\nInvitation to a private post-show meet & greet with the members of Nitty Gritty Dirt Band*\nExclusive signed 8×10 photo\nCommemorative VIP laminate\n\n*Not all members may be present \nVIP2: The Nitty Gritty Premium Seat with Meet & Greet Experience   $229  \nIncludes: \n\nPremium reserved ticket in first ten (10) rows\nInvitation to a private post-show meet & greet with the members of Nitty Gritty Dirt Band*\nExclusive signed 8×10 photo\nCommemorative VIP laminate\n\n*Not all members may be present \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/all-the-good-times-the-farewell-tour-60-years-of-dirt/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/NGDB_Concessions-Events-and-News-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
