X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/parachute-play-148008"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Parachute Play
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260413T101500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260413T104500
UID:8afc9aaddcec2c1fff20ca12d6d8ede4@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nJoin us for a cooperative m
 ovement program where we will use our imaginations while we play with a pa
 rachute! Stories and songs will be incorporated\, while we move about and 
 use our motor skills. A great activity for young children and their adults
  to come together and share an exciting and engaging play experience! (Mus
 t be 18 months-younger 3 years old with an adult\, adult involvement is re
 quired)Adults attending with their child(ren) do NOT need to register. Ple
 ase add any additional registrants to your registration if more than one c
 hild that will be participating in the program.Registration will open at 9
 :00AM on Wednesday\, April 1st for Manheim Township and East Lampeter resi
 dents and on Friday\, April 3rd for residents of other municipalities.Stor
 ytime PoliciesNo Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registration for
  more than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from registeri
 ng for future programs for a period of one month’s time. Please cancel y
 our registrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of the program to al
 low for those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in regist
 ration status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the star
 t of the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The program
  will begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your spot will
  be forfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spot
 s remain\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, registra
 nts will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start ti
 me.Accompanying Adults – This program is for adults and children to enjo
 y together. Please plan to attend and be engaged with your child. Drop off
 s will not be permitted.Cancellations- Please check your email prior to de
 parting to verify that the program has not been cancelled.Program Limits -
  Patrons are limited to one session of multiple session programs per week.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/parachute-play-148008
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
