BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/preschool-party-148758"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Preschool Party
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260414T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260414T114500
UID:3353adfd477d90d01c437ef5fee01e92@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Children\n\nJoin Ms. Laura for a fun and engaging 
 preschool program designed to spark curiosity and a love for learning in y
 oung children! This program features stories\, songs\, and hands-on activi
 ties tailored for preschool-aged kids. Each session focuses on building ea
 rly literacy\, motor skills\, and social interaction through playful explo
 ration.Perfect for ages 3–6 with an adult\, this program provides a welc
 oming and inclusive environment where kids can learn and grow together. Pa
 rents and caregivers are encouraged to participate and share in the joy of
  discovery with their little ones.Ms. Laura has over 20 years of preschool
  classroom experience bringing a wealth of knowledge in early childhood de
 velopment. Her approach focuses on creating a warm\, engaging\, and suppor
 tive environment where children can thrive.Adults attending with their chi
 ld(ren) do NOT need to register. Please add any additional registrants to 
 your registration if more than one child that will be participating in the
  program.Registration will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, April 1st for Man
 heim Township and East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, April 3rd for re
 sidents of other municipalities.Storytime PoliciesNo Show – Patrons fail
 ing to cancel their registration for more than 2 library programs in a mon
 th will be restricted from registering for future programs for a period of
  one month’s time. Please cancel your registrations at least 2 hours pri
 or to the start of the program to allow for those on the waiting list to b
 e notified of their change in registration status.Late Arrivals – Please
  arrive 10 minutes prior to the start of the program to allow for parking 
 and other circumstances. The program will begin promptly at the designated
  time. At this time\, your spot will be forfeited to those on the wait lis
 t who will be granted entry. If spots remain\, registrants may be allowed 
 into the program. However\, registrants will not be permitted to enter the
  program 5 minutes past the start time.Accompanying Adults – This progra
 m is for adults and children to enjoy together. Please plan to attend and 
 be engaged with your child. Drop offs will not be permitted.Cancellations-
  Please check your email prior to departing to verify that the program has
  not been cancelled.Program Limits - Patrons are limited to one session of
  multiple session programs per week.Preschool Party Registration Requireme
 nts – All children who will be participating in the craft will need to b
 e registered as a participant to allow for adequate supplies.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/preschool-party-148758
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
