BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Fig Lancaster": "https://figlancaster.com/event/spring-is-in-the-air-moss-wall-workshop/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:figlancaster
X-SOURCE:Fig Lancaster
X-SOURCE-URL:https://figlancaster.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260415T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260415T183000
DTSTAMP:20260403T224922
CREATED:20260315T143837Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T200104Z
UID:10014498-1776274200-1776277800@figlancaster.com
SUMMARY:Spring is in the Air Moss Wall Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Design a framed moss wall with preserved moss\, botanicals\, and two air plants in this hands-on\, guided workshop.\nUnwind at the end of your day and join us for an intimate happy hour workshop with expert instruction. As always\, BYOB.\nCreate a one-of-a-kind moss wall that brings texture\, nature\, and art together in a beautiful\, modern way.\nIn this hands-on workshop\, you’ll design a framed moss wall using a thoughtfully curated selection of preserved moss\, dried elements\, and botanical accents. Two air plants will be incorporated into your piece\, adding sculptural dimension and a living touch to your finished design.\nOur very own featured moss wall artist\, Laura Alvis\, will guide you through the creative process\, offering styling tips\, composition guidance\, and design insight along the way. Whether your aesthetic leans minimal and modern or lush and layered\, you’ll have the support to make it uniquely yours. \n            \n        \n                \n                \n    Register Now
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/spring-is-in-the-air-moss-wall-workshop/
LOCATION:Gallery Grow\, 320 North Queen Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Education & Classes
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://fig.guide/content/uploads/sites/3/2026/03/Moss-Wall-header.avif
END:VEVENT
