SUMMARY:Trivia Night at Southern Market - Meet People Lancaster team
DESCRIPTION:Meet People Lancaster\nDo you love trivia nights\, but want to
  avoid the hassle of trying to wrangle up enough friends to field a team? 
 Come play for a Meet People Lancaster team and make some new friends along
  the way!\nCost: FREE\nBar & food stations are all walk up. You’ll be on
  your own tab for the night.\nHost: Mark Aumen\nPlease try to get there by
  6:30PM\, so we can get situated at a couple tables. Trivia starts at 7PM.
  If you come up early you’ll have time to mingle and get some food befor
 e trivia starts.\nLocation: 100 S Queen St\, Lancaster\, PA 17603\nHow to 
 find the group: We have a couple acrylic sign holders on tables with Meet 
 People Lancaster logos in them. We’ll also post an Instagram story with 
 a picture of where your host\, Mark\, is sitting in the food court. Please
  follow Instagram stories for event updates. Not just for this event\, but
  for all events.
