DESCRIPTION:Community\, Everyone\n\nWant to get rid of your old books sust
 ainably? Come swap your pre-loved books for a new-to-you book from the Jul
 iana Bookstore!Stop by  any time throughout the swap to bring your book to
  share\, write a note to its next owner about why you like it\, and spend 
 the rest of the time choosing your new book and chatting with other partic
 ipants.Books brought to the exchange should be:Gently used or newNo magazi
 nes or reference books
