DTSTAMP:20260404T024946Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T120000
SUMMARY:Creative Release Open Studio Saturday
DESCRIPTION:The Creative House of Lancaster\n#### ***A Place to Make Art T
 ogether***\n\n**When:** Every Other Saturday from 10am - 12pm\n**Where:** 
 [The Candy Factory](https://share.google/nqC7VtCS6IcDeBRyg)\n**Cost:** Fre
 e & Open to the Public\n**Ages:** All Ages\n\n**Upcoming Dates**\nApril 18
 \, May 2\, May 16\, May 30\, June 13\, June 27\, July 11\, July 25\, Aug 8
 \, Aug 22\, Sept 5\, Sept 19\, Oct 3\, Oct 17\, Oct 31\, Nov 14\, Nov 28\,
  Dec 9\, Dec 23\n\n*Do you have creative aspirations but never seem to mak
 e the time? Do you want the companionship of others to overcome your creat
 ive blocks and “just do it”?*\n\nCreative Release provides spaces and 
 resources that make artmaking accessible. Whether you’re an experienced 
 artist or just looking to explore your creative side\, Creative Release is
  a safe place to explore your ideas with others. Bring your ongoing projec
 ts or use the art materials available.\n\nDon't have a project at the mome
 nt? That's just fine. I’ll have materials to share.\n**What to Expect:**
 \n\n* A welcoming\, inclusive environment\n* A variety of art materials to
  experiment with\n* Demonstrations on how to use different art materials\n
 * The opportunity to work on your personal projects\n* The chance to meet 
 and collaborate with fellow creatives\n* A moment to relax\, create\, and 
 escape the usual routine\n\n**Who Should Join?**\nAnyone and everyone! Bri
 ng an idea for a card\, a knitting pattern you’ve been wanting to try\, 
 a shirt that needs mending\, or a full-on canvas and paints. Most of all\,
  bring your lovely self! We believe in the power of community and creativi
 ty.\n\n[Event Link](https://www.jodavis.art/community-events-1/creative-re
 lease)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/event
 s/314110338/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T192521Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T192521Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
