X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/ready-set-go-kindergarten-readiness-160861"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Ready\, Set\, Go! Kindergarten Readiness
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260420T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260420T120000
UID:4326ee3363ea08d9263c08ad0d8eb873@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Children\n\nThis program is focused on developing 
 skills to prepare children who will be entering Kindergarten in the fall o
 f 2026. Children will attend this program independently and should not be 
 putting things in their mouths. Adults will be required to remain in the C
 hildren's Library during the program and will be invited in the last 5 min
 utes to review lessons taught that day and skills to be practice at home. 
 Please use the special notes section of the program registration to let us
  know if your child needs any considerations or accommodations.Be aware\, 
 this program is for 5 sessions. (April 6\, 13\, 20\, 27 and May 4). Failur
 e to attend the first of the series will result in forfeiting your spot to
  someone on the waitlist.Registration will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, M
 arch 18th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter residents and on Friday\,
  March 20th for residents of other municipalities.Laura has two decades of
  experience in preschool education. She is gifted at captivating young min
 ds with engaging and interactive content. With her knowledge and understan
 ding of child development\, she will present lessons and activities that w
 ill stimulate curiosity\, foster creativity\, and nurture social and emoti
 onal skills. Laura has a remarkable ability to communicate complex concept
 s in simple\, age-appropriate ways\, creating a dynamic learning environme
 nt where every child feels valued and supported. Your child will experienc
 e a memorable program that makes learning fun!
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/ready-set-go-kindergarte
 n-readiness-160861
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
