X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Mickey's Black Box": "https://mickeysblackbox.com/event/magnolia-park-nights-after-vamp-tour/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:mickeysblackbox
X-SOURCE:Mickey's Black Box
X-SOURCE-URL:https://mickeysblackbox.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260422T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260422T230000
DTSTAMP:20260403T224923
CREATED:20251117T150038Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260325T150814Z
UID:10000750-1776882600-1776898800@mickeysblackbox.com
SUMMARY:Magnolia Park - Nights After VAMP Tour *sold out!*
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday April 22nd\, 2026\nThis event is sold out!\nDoors | 6:30 PM\nShow | 7:30 PM \nGeneral Admission Standing Room | $33.65 + Fees\nReserved Balcony & Mezzanine Seating | $44.40 + Fees \n+$5 on All Day of Show Purchases\nThis event is all ages – 21+ With Valid ID to Drink\nCome hungry! Snacks and light bites will be available at the canteen.\n—————————————————\nPresented by Big Fan Presents\n—————————————————\nMagnolia Park is a five piece pop punk/alternative rock band from Orlando\, Florida. The band blends elements of hip hop\, pop punk and Emo rock to create a captivating sound and haunting aesthetic. Their music is produced by legendary alternative rock/pop punk producer Andrew Wade of The Audio Compound\, who has worked with bands like A Day To Remember\, Neck Deep\, Wage War\, Real Friends\, and more.  Magnolia Park started in Late 2018 by Tristan Torres and Freddie Criales in a staples parking lot where Tristan used to work.  \nClick here to purchase the VIP Experience. \nCheck out Magnolia Park here!\nWebsite | Instagram | Instagram \nSupported by: Silly Goose & Pink Noise\n—————————————————\n*Ticket Alert*  \nTickets for Mickey’s Black Box are sold through TicketMaster\, via our website\, or in person at our Box Office. Any tickets purchased elsewhere will not be honored and we are not responsible for tickets purchased from any 3rd party sellers.  Do not google the name of the band to search for tickets.  Go to Mickeysblackbox.com ONLY. Mickeysblackbox.com will never direct you anywhere but the official TicketMaster event site. \n\nAll bags are subject are to search upon entry. Tickets are non-refundable\, save for instances in which performances are cancelled by Mickey’s Black Box. For more information about our venue\, please visit the FAQ page of our website: https://mickeysblackbox.com/faq/ or call our box office line at (717) 723 – 8463.
URL:https://mickeysblackbox.com/event/magnolia-park-nights-after-vamp-tour/
LOCATION:Mickey’s Black Box\, 101 Rock Lititz Boulevard\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mickeysblackbox.com/app/uploads/2025/11/1Y1A3781-scaled-e1771481235208.jpg
END:VEVENT
