 iting\, creating\, or updating a resume?Applying for jobs online? Filling 
 out clearances/forms to begin employment?Learning how to write\, reply to\
 , and delete emails?Using Microsoft Word\, Excel\, Power Point\, or Outloo
 k more proficiently?Using virtual tools such as Zoom or Microsoft Teams?Le
 arning how to stay safe while shopping online?Creating and using an email 
 account?Turning on a computer and connecting to the Internet?Using the Int
 ernet safely and protecting your information?Unbox Your New Tech Consider 
 stopping in at the Columbia Public Library for FREE one-on-one assistance.
  Doran is available every Tuesday\, Wednesday\, and Thursday 10:00am - 3:0
 0pm to assist you.Phillip is available Monday\, Wednesday\, and Friday 10:
 00am - 1:00pm to assist you. Bring your own laptop or use one of ours at t
 he library. Appointments are recommended but not required. If you'd like t
 o set up an appointment with Doran\, please email: doran.condon@millersvil
 le.edu or call 717-871-5951.
