SUMMARY:Shenandoah
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $39 $49 $59 $79\n \nFor more than 30 years\, Grammy Award-winning country band Shenandoah has delivered heartfelt songs and rich harmonies that helped shape the sound of modern country music. Led by original frontman Marty Raybon\, the group rose to fame with beloved hits like “Two Dozen Roses\,” “Church on Cumberland Road\,” “Next to You\, Next to Me\,” and “I Want to Be Loved Like That.” \nKnown for their genuine lyrics and timeless sound\, Shenandoah continues to captivate audiences with a mix of nostalgia and new energy. Experience an evening filled with classic favorites and the unmistakable charm of one of country music’s most enduring groups. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
