 tion? --Are you looking for a fun night for your family\, friends\, or emp
 loyees? Participants will need to communicate and work as a team to solve 
 puzzles and tasks within 60 minutes to save the library. Join us for an Es
 cape Room created and produced by the Junior Friends of the Ephrata Public
  Library! This fundraiser benefits the Ephrata Public Library.Akron Boroug
 h is matching the funds raised to help the Jr. Friends purchase 4 new book
