  from 10-1 in Morgan Center C.Note: This is a self-directed community grou
 p. While no formal instructor is provided\, players of all levels are welc
 ome to learn from one another. What to Bring: Sets and racks (at least one
  per four players)Your current 2026 National Mah Jongg League cardA friend
 ly\, patient attitude! Community GuidelinesBe Welcoming:  We all started a
