UID:8c0e232b72cd783f48846e00f9874c9e@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Gaming\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nEver wanted to run your own table
 top RPG but felt overwhelmed by the rulebooks? Do you have a world-buildin
 g itch that needs scratching? Join us for Game Master 101\, a crash course
  designed to turn players into Game Masters.Whether you're interested in D
 ungeons & Dragons\, Pathfinder\, or indie storytelling systems\, this work
 shop covers the essential behind the curtain magic that makes a game night
  unforgettable.What We’ll Cover:How to start a session that grabs your p
 layers immediately.Balancing game mechanics with creative storytelling.Bui
 lding memorable characters that aren't just quest-givers.Tips for pacing\,
  player engagement\, and handling the unexpected (because players will set
  your tavern on fire).Resources and apps to make your life easier.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Morgan Center C
