SUMMARY:Creative Release Open Studio Saturday
DESCRIPTION:The Creative House of Lancaster\n#### ***A Place to Make Art T
 ogether***\n\n**When:** Every Other Saturday from 10am - 12pm\n**Where:** 
 [The Candy Factory](https://share.google/nqC7VtCS6IcDeBRyg)\n**Cost:** Fre
 e & Open to the Public\n**Ages:** All Ages\n\n**Upcoming Dates**\nMay 16\,
  May 30\, June 13\, June 27\, July 11\, July 25\, Aug 8\, Aug 22\, Sept 5\
 , Sept 19\, Oct 3\, Oct 17\, Oct 31\, Nov 14\, Nov 28\, Dec 9\, Dec 23\n\n
 *Do you have creative aspirations but never seem to make the time? Do you 
 want the companionship of others to overcome your creative blocks and “j
 ust do it”?*\n\nCreative Release provides spaces and resources that make
  artmaking accessible. Whether you’re an experienced artist or just look
 ing to explore your creative side\, Creative Release is a safe place to ex
 plore your ideas with others. Bring your ongoing projects or use the art m
 aterials available.\n\nDon't have a project at the moment? That's just fin
 e. I’ll have materials to share.\n**What to Expect:**\n\n* A welcoming\,
  inclusive environment\n* A variety of art materials to experiment with\n*
  Demonstrations on how to use different art materials\n* The opportunity t
 o work on your personal projects\n* The chance to meet and collaborate wit
 h fellow creatives\n* A moment to relax\, create\, and escape the usual ro
 utine\n\n**Who Should Join?**\nAnyone and everyone! Bring an idea for a ca
 rd\, a knitting pattern you’ve been wanting to try\, a shirt that needs 
 mending\, or a full-on canvas and paints. Most of all\, bring your lovely 
 self! We believe in the power of community and creativity.\n\n[Event Link]
 (https://www.jodavis.art/community-events-1/creative-release)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/event
 s/314110363/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T192929Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T192929Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
