 e.🍽️Cooks & Books is an opportunity for passionate home cooks to gath
 er around the table for conversation over a potluck feast of delicious foo
 d made from the recipes of a featured chef\, food blog\, or cookbook. Why 
 not invite a friend to join you? The more\, the merrier!Attendees\, who sh
 ould be 14 years of age or older\, are asked to bring a dish to share. Veg
 an/vegetarian recipes are welcome. Please bring your own serving utensils\
 , place setting\, and beverage.New and experienced cooks are welcome! The 
 event is free\, but reservations are required! Please cancel your registra
 tion if you cannot attend!
