  a morning of strategy\, skill\, and socializing! 🀄️✨Whether you ar
 e a seasoned pro or a newcomer looking to practice\, come enjoy the classi
 c game of tiles in a friendly\, community-led atmosphere\, every Wednesday
  from 10-1 in Morgan Center C.Note: This is a self-directed community grou
 p. While no formal instructor is provided\, players of all levels are welc
 ome to learn from one another. What to Bring: Sets and racks (at least one
  per four players)Your current 2026 National Mah Jongg League cardA friend
 ly\, patient attitude! Community GuidelinesBe Welcoming:  We all started a
 s beginners! Please be patient with those still learning to playThe "Rule 
 of Five": If a fifth player joins your table\, we suggest the "East Sits O
 ut" rotation—the player in the East position rotates out for one hand so
