DESCRIPTION:Community\, Storytime\, Babies\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nIntrod
 uce literacy and learning to your little one with a community in the Libra
 ry! We will occasionally make messy art\, including sensory experiences th
 at are always optional. After reading a few stories we will enjoy lots of 
 peer playtime! This session will focus on healthy coping skills\, emotiona
 l regulation and behavior management. Jada Morales from CAP Lanc. will pro
 vide resources to families\, including Domestic Violence Services. We are 
 a proud Family Place Library\, which our focus is on providing families wi
 th further education on their child and encouragement for partnership in t
 he community. Ages 0-5.
LOCATION:Ephrata\, EPH 1/2 Multipurpose Room Kitchen Side
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/baby-book-club-157133
