 intersection of artificial intelligence and digital platforms\, examining 
 how algorithms shape user behavior\, content creation\, and online communi
 ties. We will review the ethical implications of AI-driven social media an
 d gain some practical skills to navigate these evolving technologies. This
  class is supported by a grant from the OpenAI Foundation. Ages 18+.
