UID:6593e4b36e03c9482680d3f736cd5aa0@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Babies\n\nBook Babies is a special time for babies
  to share stories\, songs\, rhymes and games with their grown-ups. Come pl
 ay with us in the Children’s Library! (Newborn to 17 months\, with adult
 ) Please add any additional registrants to your registration if more than 
 one child that will be participating in the program.Registration for Book 
 Babies will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, April 29th for Manheim Township 
 and East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, May 1st for residents of other
  municipalities.Storytime PoliciesProgram Limits - Patrons are limited to 
 one session of multiple session programs per week.Cancellations- Please ch
 eck your email prior to departing to verify that the program has not been 
 cancelled.No Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registration for mor
 e than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from registering f
 or future programs for a period of one month’s time. Please cancel your 
 registrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of the program to allow 
 for those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in registrati
 on status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the start of
  the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The program wil
 l begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your spot will be 
 forfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spots re
 main\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, registrants 
 will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start time.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/book-babies-am-session-1
 48788
