 ike the ocean\, and feel the peace within us.Each session\, we will pair y
 oga-inspired movements and simple mindfulness practices with books to enga
 ge body\, heart\, and mind.Caregivers are encouraged to participate as the
 ir bodies allow.We think preschoolers (ages 3-6) will enjoy this program t
 he most\, but older and younger siblings are invited to join in on the fun
 !Thank you for completing the registration process for the child(ren) in y
