 ploads/event/2026TPAB%20Mobilize%20%285%29_20260204192917714717.png
DESCRIPTION:### Join Turn PA Blue as we make calls for the 2026 Primary El
 ection! We'll be making calls using the Scale to Win Auto-Dialer\, a compu
 ter program that dials FOR YOU! It's easy to use and allows us to have mor
 e meaningful conversations! All you need is your computer & internet acces
 s! *This phone bank is held on Zoom. At the start of the shift\, we will r
 eview the script and provide dialer training to anyone who needs it. Then 
 we'll make calls together until the end of the shift.*
LOCATION:Virtual event
