UID:9a2e24868dd340d1e3d893dbacc1249d@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Technology Class\, Adults\n\nPA CareerLink® Lancaster County 
 will be at the Quarryville Library every other Wednesday from 10 am to 3 p
 m. The navigator can help you with your job search\, leveling up your comp
 uter skills\, resume and interview tips\, career exploration\, and much mo
 re!Registration is not required at this time although we appreciate if you
  can do so. If demand for this service is strong we may institute a signup
