X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: The Creative House of Lancaster": "https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/events/314110367/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_the_creative_house_of_lancaster
X-SOURCE:Meetup: The Creative House of Lancaster
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/
UID:event_314110367@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260404T024946Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260516T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260516T120000
SUMMARY:Creative Release Open Studio Saturday
DESCRIPTION:The Creative House of Lancaster\n#### ***A Place to Make Art T
 ogether***\n\n**When:** Every Other Saturday from 10am - 12pm\n**Where:** 
 [The Candy Factory](https://share.google/nqC7VtCS6IcDeBRyg)\n**Cost:** Fre
 e & Open to the Public\n**Ages:** All Ages\n\n**Upcoming Dates**\nMay 30\,
  June 13\, June 27\, July 11\, July 25\, Aug 8\, Aug 22\, Sept 5\, Sept 19
 \, Oct 3\, Oct 17\, Oct 31\, Nov 14\, Nov 28\, Dec 9\, Dec 23\n\n*Do you h
 ave creative aspirations but never seem to make the time? Do you want the 
 companionship of others to overcome your creative blocks and “just do it
 ”?*\n\nCreative Release provides spaces and resources that make artmakin
 g accessible. Whether you’re an experienced artist or just looking to ex
 plore your creative side\, Creative Release is a safe place to explore you
 r ideas with others. Bring your ongoing projects or use the art materials 
 available.\n\nDon't have a project at the moment? That's just fine. I’ll
  have materials to share.\n**What to Expect:**\n\n* A welcoming\, inclusiv
 e environment\n* A variety of art materials to experiment with\n* Demonstr
 ations on how to use different art materials\n* The opportunity to work on
  your personal projects\n* The chance to meet and collaborate with fellow 
 creatives\n* A moment to relax\, create\, and escape the usual routine\n\n
 **Who Should Join?**\nAnyone and everyone! Bring an idea for a card\, a kn
 itting pattern you’ve been wanting to try\, a shirt that needs mending\,
  or a full-on canvas and paints. Most of all\, bring your lovely self! We 
 believe in the power of community and creativity.\n\n[Event Link](https://
 www.jodavis.art/community-events-1/creative-release)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/event
 s/314110367/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T193038Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T193038Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
