 n ages 2-7! Using colorful Lego Duplo blocks\, kids can explore their crea
 tivity\, improve fine motor skills\, and build their imagination through h
 ands-on play. This program encourages collaborative play and parent-child 
 interaction.Perfect for young builders of all skill levels\, this free pro
 gram offers a relaxed and welcoming environment for families to connect an
 d create together. Come play\, learn\, and grow at the library! Each famil
 y group must include a responsible adult in the room at all times. This pr
 ogram is for children 2 to 7 years old only! While other ages are welcome 
