BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/parachute-play-148013"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Parachute Play
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260518T101500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260518T104500
UID:1990e8b23bfa4eec81b7c7a221e9b087@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nJoin us for a cooperative m
 ovement program where we will use our imaginations while we play with a pa
 rachute! Stories and songs will be incorporated\, while we move about and 
 use our motor skills. A great activity for young children and their adults
  to come together and share an exciting and engaging play experience! (Mus
 t be 18 months-younger 3 years old with an adult\, adult involvement is re
 quired)Adults attending with their child(ren) do NOT need to register. Ple
 ase add any additional registrants to your registration if more than one c
 hild that will be participating in the program.Registration will open at 9
 :00AM on Wednesday\, May 6th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter reside
 nts and on Friday\, May 8th for residents of other municipalities.Storytim
 e PoliciesNo Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registration for mor
 e than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from registering f
 or future programs for a period of one month’s time. Please cancel your 
 registrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of the program to allow 
 for those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in registrati
 on status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the start of
  the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The program wil
 l begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your spot will be 
 forfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spots re
 main\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, registrants 
 will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start time.A
 ccompanying Adults – This program is for adults and children to enjoy to
 gether. Please plan to attend and be engaged with your child. Drop offs wi
 ll not be permitted.Cancellations- Please check your email prior to depart
 ing to verify that the program has not been cancelled.Program Limits - Pat
 rons are limited to one session of multiple session programs per week.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/parachute-play-148013
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
