BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/bad-art-club-153026"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Bad Art Club
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260520T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260520T200000
UID:e1dd04436c5df1caa7c11827b290c2c4@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Arts & Crafts\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nWhether you’re a seasone
 d creative struggling with art block or an arts enthusiast who's never pic
 ked up a pencil. Bad Art Club encourages you to release your fears\, doubt
 s and/or perfectionistic tendencies. Instead\, give yourself permission to
  play\, make mistakes\, have fun\, and just make bad art.THANK YOU for reg
 istering -- it will help us determine how many supplies we need! · Ages 1
 8+Monthly Projects:January: A game of Pictionary (to celebrate the first c
 lub meet-up)February: Collage Night: Our Inner GardenMarch: Paint and Swap
  Night    April: Found PoetryMay: Play with Clay DoughJune: Blind Contour 
 Art ChallengeJuly: Paint Night (Randomizer Challenge)August: Collage Night
 : Play September: Judge a Book by Its CoverOctober: Exquisite CorpseNovemb
 er: PictionaryDecember: DIY Card Deck (affirmation cards\, oracle cards\, 
 etc.)
LOCATION:Lancaster\, LPL Community Room
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/bad-art-club-153026
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
