 l hold regular monthly meetings in 2026 at 7:00 P.M. (prevailing time): Ja
 nuary 21\, February 18\, March 18\, April 15\, May 20\, June 17\, July 15\
 , August 19\, September 16\, October 21\, November 18\, December 16\, and 
 January 20\, 2027. The Library will hold its regular Annual Meeting at 6:0
 0 P.M. on January 20\, 2027. Meetings will be held at 11 Chestnut Drive\, 
 New Holland\, PA\, 17557 or\, if conditions require\, virtually.  Visit el
 ancolibrary.org for location information. All meetings are open to the pub
 lic.
