UID:0e794215c72d5f80101b809d34e89168@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Adults\n\nIf you are a victim of domestic violence
 \, hope and help is out there! Talk to Domestic Violence Services team mem
 bers from Community Action Partnership to learn about the resources they o
 ffer\, including crisis intervention\, safety planning\, safe housing opti
 ons\, and other forms of support.
