BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/sensory-friendly-free-create-157395"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:The Sensory Social
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260521T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260521T140000
UID:65f1b521b01e24d4be2af3b9f49d40fd@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Arts & Crafts\, Community\, Adults\n\nLooking for a place to r
 elax\, tinker\, and meet new people? The Sensory Social is a low-stress ha
 ngout for neurodivergent adults. We’ve gathered a variety of tactile and
  creative stations for you to explore at your own pace.Enjoy our sequin wa
 ll\, motion bubblers\, and fidget kits\, or try your hand at the knit boar
 d and art stations. This is a self-guided\, 'choose your own adventure' sp
 ace where you can be yourself among peers. If you need a hand using the ma
 terials\, please bring a friend or support person along. Come hang out and
  find what feels good!This program is designed for adult folks with IDD & 
 autism. We want everyone to participate with their peers\, regardless of m
 otor or communication skills.  Please do not remove supplies from the room
 .
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Morgan Center B
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/sensory-friendly-free-cr
 eate-157395
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/book-babies-am-session-148790"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Book Babies AM Session
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260521T101500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260521T110000
UID:4a837eb295a095d96901d2d3b1f68078@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Babies\n\nBook Babies is a special time for babies
  to share stories\, songs\, rhymes and games with their grown-ups. Come pl
 ay with us in the Children’s Library! (Newborn to 17 months\, with adult
 ) Please add any additional registrants to your registration if more than 
 one child that will be participating in the program.Registration for Book 
 Babies will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, May 13th for Manheim Township an
 d East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, May 15th for residents of other 
 municipalities.Storytime PoliciesProgram Limits - Patrons are limited to o
 ne session of multiple session programs per week.Cancellations- Please che
 ck your email prior to departing to verify that the program has not been c
 ancelled.No Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registration for more
  than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from registering fo
 r future programs for a period of one month’s time. Please cancel your r
 egistrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of the program to allow f
 or those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in registratio
 n status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the start of 
 the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The program will
  begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your spot will be f
 orfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spots rem
 ain\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, registrants w
 ill not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start time.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/book-babies-am-session-1
 48790
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
