 ) do NOT need to register. Please add any additional registrants to your r
 egistration if more than one child that will be participating in the progr
 am.Registration will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, May 13th for Manheim To
 wnship and East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, May 15th for residents 
 of other municipalities.Storytime PoliciesNo Show – Patrons failing to c
 ancel their registration for more than 2 library programs in a month will 
