SUMMARY:Creative Release Open Studio Saturday
DESCRIPTION:The Creative House of Lancaster\n#### ***A Place to Make Art T
 ogether***\n\n**When:** Every Other Saturday from 10am - 12pm\n**Where:** 
 [The Candy Factory](https://share.google/nqC7VtCS6IcDeBRyg)\n**Cost:** Fre
 e & Open to the Public\n**Ages:** All Ages\n\n**Upcoming Dates**\nJune 13\
 , June 27\, July 11\, July 25\, Aug 8\, Aug 22\, Sept 5\, Sept 19\, Oct 3\
 , Oct 17\, Oct 31\, Nov 14\, Nov 28\, Dec 9\, Dec 23\n\n*Do you have creat
 ive aspirations but never seem to make the time? Do you want the companion
 ship of others to overcome your creative blocks and “just do it”?*\n\n
 Creative Release provides spaces and resources that make artmaking accessi
 ble. Whether you’re an experienced artist or just looking to explore you
 r creative side\, Creative Release is a safe place to explore your ideas w
 ith others. Bring your ongoing projects or use the art materials available
 .\n\nDon't have a project at the moment? That's just fine. I’ll have mat
 erials to share.\n**What to Expect:**\n\n* A welcoming\, inclusive environ
 ment\n* A variety of art materials to experiment with\n* Demonstrations on
  how to use different art materials\n* The opportunity to work on your per
 sonal projects\n* The chance to meet and collaborate with fellow creatives
 \n* A moment to relax\, create\, and escape the usual routine\n\n**Who Sho
 uld Join?**\nAnyone and everyone! Bring an idea for a card\, a knitting pa
 ttern you’ve been wanting to try\, a shirt that needs mending\, or a ful
 l-on canvas and paints. Most of all\, bring your lovely self! We believe i
 n the power of community and creativity.\n\n[Event Link](https://www.jodav
 is.art/community-events-1/creative-release)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/event
 s/314110371/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T193115Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T193115Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
