DESCRIPTION:Our theory of change lies in having person-to-person conversat
 ions that dismantle fear and division within our community. When we can ha
 ve open conversations without judgement\, stigma\, or fear - moving toward
 s empathy and a consideration of progressive solutions\, we can learn more
  about the lived experiences of our neighbors and begin the process of lon
 g lasting political change in Lancaster. This Spring\, we will be launchin
 g a rigorous and intentional deep canvassing program throughout the coun
LOCATION:"The Underground"\, 53 N Duke St 10\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602
