DESCRIPTION:Arts & Crafts\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nKnitting Club meets the 1s
 t and 3rd Monday of the month\, from 10 a.m. until noon and the second and
  last Tuesday of each month from 6 p.m. – 7:30 p.m.  Knitting Club is fo
 r people who knit and like to share the craft. This is not a class or inst
 ruction\, just a friendly gathering to knit and work on projects. Must bri
