BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"American Music Theatre": "https://amtshows.com/show/scotty-mccreery-live-in-concert-2026/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:amtshows
X-SOURCE:American Music Theatre
X-SOURCE-URL:https://amtshows.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260606T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260606T193000
DTSTAMP:20260403T224933
CREATED:20260105T143059Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260109T150256Z
UID:10001844-1780774200-1780774200@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:Scotty McCreery Live in Concert
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $59 $79 $99 $109\nAMT Member Pre-Sale: Wednesday\, January 7 at 10:00 a.m.\nPublic On-Sale: Friday\, January 9 at 10:00 a.m. \nWith his warm baritone\, easy charm\, and authentic country roots\, Scotty McCreery has become one of today’s most beloved voices in country music. His chart-topping albums\, multi-platinum singles\, and heartfelt storytelling have earned him a devoted following and a standout place on the country music landscape. \nFans will hear favorites like “Five More Minutes\,” “Damn Strait\,” and “This Is It\,” along with the sincerity and energy that define Scotty’s live performances. His blend of tradition\, contemporary style\, and personal\, relatable lyrics creates a concert experience that resonates long after the last note. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/scotty-mccreery-live-in-concert-2026/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SM_Website-News-Post-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"American Music Theatre": "https://amtshows.com/show/righteous-brothers-lovin-feeling-farewell-tour-2026/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:amtshows
X-SOURCE:American Music Theatre
X-SOURCE-URL:https://amtshows.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260607T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260607T150000
DTSTAMP:20260403T224933
CREATED:20251013T133048Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251107T200142Z
UID:10001824-1780844400-1780844400@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:The Righteous Brothers: Lovin' Feelin' Farewell Tour
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $49 $59 $69 $79 \nPrepare for a soul-stirring\, nostalgic concert experience at the Lovin’ Feelin’ Farewell Tour of the legendary Righteous Brothers. The Righteous Brothers Lovin’ Feelin’ Farewell Tour promises a captivating musical odyssey\, spanning the early days of rock and roll\, the era of Blue-Eyed Soul and as far reaching as the movie Dirty Dancing. From heartwarming ballads to energetic rock anthems\, every performance is a testament to the enduring power of The Righteous Brothers’ music and their connection to fans across the globe. \nTake a journey through decades of timeless hits that have defined a generation\, including “You’ve Lost That Lovin’ Feelin\,'” “Unchained Melody\,” “(I’ve Had) The Time of My Life\,” “Soul and Inspiration\,” “Ebb Tide\,” and “Rock and Roll Heaven.” \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/righteous-brothers-lovin-feeling-farewell-tour-2026/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/News-Post-and-Event-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
