SUMMARY:Creative Release Open Studio Saturday
DESCRIPTION:The Creative House of Lancaster\n#### ***A Place to Make Art T
 ogether***\n\n**When:** Every Other Saturday from 10am - 12pm\n**Where:** 
 [The Candy Factory](https://share.google/nqC7VtCS6IcDeBRyg)\n**Cost:** Fre
 e & Open to the Public\n**Ages:** All Ages\n\n**Upcoming Dates**\nJune 27\
 , July 11\, July 25\, Aug 8\, Aug 22\, Sept 5\, Sept 19\, Oct 3\, Oct 17\,
  Oct 31\, Nov 14\, Nov 28\, Dec 9\, Dec 23\n\n*Do you have creative aspira
 tions but never seem to make the time? Do you want the companionship of ot
 hers to overcome your creative blocks and “just do it”?*\n\nCreative R
 elease provides spaces and resources that make artmaking accessible. Wheth
 er you’re an experienced artist or just looking to explore your creative
  side\, Creative Release is a safe place to explore your ideas with others
 . Bring your ongoing projects or use the art materials available.\n\nDon't
  have a project at the moment? That's just fine. I’ll have materials to 
 share.\n**What to Expect:**\n\n* A welcoming\, inclusive environment\n* A 
 variety of art materials to experiment with\n* Demonstrations on how to us
 e different art materials\n* The opportunity to work on your personal proj
 ects\n* The chance to meet and collaborate with fellow creatives\n* A mome
 nt to relax\, create\, and escape the usual routine\n\n**Who Should Join?*
 *\nAnyone and everyone! Bring an idea for a card\, a knitting pattern you
 ’ve been wanting to try\, a shirt that needs mending\, or a full-on canv
 as and paints. Most of all\, bring your lovely self! We believe in the pow
 er of community and creativity.\n\n[Event Link](https://www.jodavis.art/co
 mmunity-events-1/creative-release)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/event
 s/314110440/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T193141Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T193141Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
