BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"American Music Theatre": "https://amtshows.com/show/straight-no-chaser-beach-bash/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:amtshows
X-SOURCE:American Music Theatre
X-SOURCE-URL:https://amtshows.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260624T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260624T193000
DTSTAMP:20260403T224933
CREATED:20260209T143030Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T144558Z
UID:10001854-1782329400-1782329400@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:Straight No Chaser: Beach Bash
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $59 $69 $79 $89\nAMT Member Presale: Wednesday\, February 11 at 9:00 a.m.\nPublic On-Sale: Friday February 13 at 10:00 a.m. \nClick Here for Artist Presale: \nIf the phrase “male a cappella group” conjures up an image of students in blue blazers\, ties\, and khakis singing traditional college songs on ivied campuses… think again. Straight No Chaser (SNC) are neither strait-laced nor straight-faced\, but neither are they vaudeville-style kitsch. They have emerged as a phenomenon with a massive fanbase and a long list of accomplishments including 2 RIAA Gold Certified albums\, over 1.5 million concert tickets sold\, over 1 billion streams on Pandora\, and over 2 million albums sold worldwide. Straight No Chaser is the real deal\, the captivating sound of nine unadulterated human voices coming together to make extraordinary music that is moving people in a fundamental sense… and with a sense of humor. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/straight-no-chaser-beach-bash/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/SNC_Concessions-Events-and-News-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Bird-in-Hand": "https://bird-in-hand.com/event/lancaster-county-carriage-antique-auction-2/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Bird-in-Hand": "https://bird-in-hand.com/event/lancaster-county-carriage-antique-auction/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bird_in_hand
X-SOURCE:Bird-in-Hand
X-SOURCE-URL:https://bird-in-hand.com/events/
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260625
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260627
DTSTAMP:20260403T224925
CREATED:20210716T122752Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T113317Z
UID:10000870-1782345600-1782518399@bird-in-hand.com
SUMMARY:Lancaster County Carriage & Antique Auction
DESCRIPTION:The Lancaster County Carriage & Antique Auction is a premier event that takes place annually on the Thursday & Friday before the last Saturday in June. There is an Early Bird Auction on Thursday afternoon and an all-day auction on Friday. \nThousands of people come to the village of Bird-in-Hand for the auction which is held on the Smucker Homestead. Equine and antique enthusiasts\, consignors\, local residents\, out-of-town visitors\, and whole families look forward to our auction each year. Many are from the East Coast\, but also from places as far away as Texas and California. \nThis is a significant fundraiser for our Hand-in-Hand Fire Company. We are appreciative of the amazing support we receive both from our local volunteers and the visitors to our area who come back year after year.
URL:https://bird-in-hand.com/event/lancaster-county-carriage-antique-auction/
LOCATION:Bird-in-Hand Events Field\, 2727 Old Philadelphia Pike\, Bird-in-Hand\, PA\, 17505\, United States
CATEGORIES:County Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bird-in-hand.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/carriage-auction-header.jpg
GEO:40.039716;-76.177661
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Bird-in-Hand Events Field 2727 Old Philadelphia Pike Bird-in-Hand PA 17505 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=2727 Old Philadelphia Pike:geo:-76.177661,40.039716
END:VEVENT
