SUMMARY:Creative Release Open Studio Saturday
DESCRIPTION:The Creative House of Lancaster\n#### ***A Place to Make Art T
 ogether***\n\n**When:** Every Other Saturday from 10am - 12pm\n**Where:** 
 [The Candy Factory](https://share.google/nqC7VtCS6IcDeBRyg)\n**Cost:** Fre
 e & Open to the Public\n**Ages:** All Ages\n\n**Upcoming Dates**\nJuly 11\
 , July 25\, Aug 8\, Aug 22\, Sept 5\, Sept 19\, Oct 3\, Oct 17\, Oct 31\, 
 Nov 14\, Nov 28\, Dec 9\, Dec 23\n\n*Do you have creative aspirations but 
 never seem to make the time? Do you want the companionship of others to ov
 ercome your creative blocks and “just do it”?*\n\nCreative Release pro
 vides spaces and resources that make artmaking accessible. Whether you’r
 e an experienced artist or just looking to explore your creative side\, Cr
 eative Release is a safe place to explore your ideas with others. Bring yo
 ur ongoing projects or use the art materials available.\n\nDon't have a pr
 oject at the moment? That's just fine. I’ll have materials to share.\n**
 What to Expect:**\n\n* A welcoming\, inclusive environment\n* A variety of
  art materials to experiment with\n* Demonstrations on how to use differen
 t art materials\n* The opportunity to work on your personal projects\n* Th
 e chance to meet and collaborate with fellow creatives\n* A moment to rela
 x\, create\, and escape the usual routine\n\n**Who Should Join?**\nAnyone 
 and everyone! Bring an idea for a card\, a knitting pattern you’ve been 
 wanting to try\, a shirt that needs mending\, or a full-on canvas and pain
 ts. Most of all\, bring your lovely self! We believe in the power of commu
 nity and creativity.\n\n[Event Link](https://www.jodavis.art/community-eve
 nts-1/creative-release)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-creative-house-of-lancaster/event
 s/314110445/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T193200Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T193200Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
