BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Zest Chef": "https://zestchef.com/class/2765-kids-camp-picnicing-and-glamping-ages-7-15/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:zestchef
X-SOURCE:Zest Chef
X-SOURCE-URL:https://zestchef.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260723T123000
DTSTAMP:20260403T224939
CREATED:20260218T014740Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260218T014740Z
UID:10000378-1784628000-1784809800@zestchef.com
SUMMARY:2765 -  Kids Camp: Picnicing and Glamping (ages 7-15)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun-filled Picnic & Camping Cooking Adventure with our wonderful kids’ instructor and artist\, Gwen Eberly! In this hands-on summer camp\, young chefs will build confidence in the kitchen while learning to prepare foods inspired by picnics\, campouts\, and outdoor cooking traditions. Each day\, campers will explore new skills\, try fresh flavors\, and create kid-friendly dishes perfect for sharing\, all in a creative\, supportive environment designed to spark curiosity and independence in the kitchen. \nHands on. Ages 7-15 \nDay 1 – 7/21 \n\nTurkey\, Cheese and Basil Pesto Wrap\nRainbow Veggie Wraps\nShredded Potato Salad\nTrail Mix\nHomemade Marshmallows\n\nDay 2 – 7/22 \n\nTaco Salad \nGrilled Corn with Cilantro Lime Dressing\nGuacamole\nS’mores Tarts with Homemade Marshmallows\n\nDay 3 – 7/23 \n\nEgg Salad Sandwich\nPressed Italian Sandwich\nPasta Salad with Tangy Vinaigrette\nChocolate Brownies
URL:https://zestchef.com/class/2765-kids-camp-picnicing-and-glamping-ages-7-15/
LOCATION:Zest Cooking School\, 1180 Erbs Quarry Road\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
CATEGORIES:Basics and Techniques,Healthy Eating,Kids & Teens,Seasonal
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://zestchef.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/picnicking-and-glamping-scaled-e1771379240458.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Scrap & Craft": "https://www.meetup.com/scrapandcraft/events/xvnsvqyjckbcc/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_scrapandcraft
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Scrap & Craft
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/scrapandcraft/
UID:event_xvnsvqyjckbcc@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260404T024947Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T220000
SUMMARY:Lancaster Scrapbooking & Papercrafting Monthly gathering
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Scrapbooking\, Cards & Papercrafts\nScrapbook\, make
  cards\, practice quilling\, or paint!\nMeeting on the third Tuesday\, 6-1
 0 p.m.\, at the Cozy Crop House. (Also meeting the next night\, Wednesday\
 , same time & place. You can come to one or both\, and can leave your gear
  overnight.) A chance to meet & gather monthly with local scrapbookers & c
 rafters\, in an ideal crafting environment! Plenty of room to do your own 
 thing while we socialize. Bring your own supplies & projects\, or just sit
  back and relax with scrapping friends\, and watch & learn a new technique
 .\nSpecific crafting events (eg. card classes\, paint nights\, etc) may be
  featured here as scheduled.\nBring snacks to share if you wish.\nMeetup g
 roups are charged a monthly administration fee which is currently paid in 
 this group by a few members. VOLUNTARY donations of $1 or $2 into a group 
 "kitty" will help us continue the group's open membership and online adver
 tising. The rate it costs our _whole group_ is about $12/month for a 6-mon
 th commitment. Please do not feel you cannot come if you don't contribute-
 -the fee is paid\, and donations are voluntary to cover future fees.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/scrapandcraft/events/xvnsvqyjckbcc/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20190405T040038Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20190405T040038Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
