DTSTAMP:20260404T024943Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260918T073000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260918T083000
SUMMARY:Data Lancaster Coffee Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Data Lancaster\nWe meet up at the Mean Cup coffee shop and cha
 t about whatever topics come to mind. Attendees tend to work in data-relat
 ed jobs\, so expect at least some data-related discussions\, and attendees
  sharing what they've been up to on the data-related projects they're work
 ing on is common.\n\nBe sure to join the Data Lancaster Meetup group in or
 der to receive notifications of future events!\n\n*(And if you have a conf
 lict this month and want to plan for the future\, we meet the third Friday
  of the month every month except November and December)*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/data-lancaster/events/312776850/
